::Amperion::
    He wakes up again.  This time he stands up.  His entire back is screaming 
with pain.  He looks around and sees Grimmler and Slashstrike standing there. 
 "Would one of you mind giving me a hand."  With that he collapses again and 
falls toward Grimmler.
